---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';

// 수식 변수
const mathMain = "$ f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\displaystyle \\frac{x^2+ax+b}{x-2} & (x \\neq 2) \\\\ 5 & (x = 2) \\end{cases} $";
const mathStep1 = "$ f(2) = \\lim_{x \\to 2} f(x) $";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 10. 고난도 미정계수 - 상세 연습</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			/* [표준 디자인 시스템] KaTeX & 모바일 수식 최적화 */
			.formula-box {
				text-align: center;
				margin: 30px 0;
				background: #fff;
				padding: 30px;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
				overflow: hidden;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.math-container {
				width: 100%;
				overflow-x: auto;
				white-space: nowrap;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.katex-display {
				margin: 0.5em 0 !important;
				overflow-x: auto;
				overflow-y: hidden;
			}
			@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
				.formula-box { padding: 15px 5px !important; margin: 20px 0 !important; }
				.katex-display { font-size: 0.85em !important; }
				.formula-box p { font-size: 1rem !important; line-height: 1.5; }
				body { padding: 10px; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 10. 고난도 미정계수" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">💡 수능 출제 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>함숫값과 극한값이 같음을 정의로 접근</li>
					<li>분수 식의 미정계수 결정 원리</li>
					<li>복합적인 계산 능력 요구</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						[핵심 문제]
					</h4>
					<p>함수 $f(x)$가 $x=2$에서 연속일 때, $a+b$의 값을 구하시오.</p>

					<div class="formula-box">
						<div class="math-container">
							<span set:html={"$$ f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\displaystyle \\frac{x^2+ax+b}{x-2} & (x \\neq 2) \\\\ 5 & (x = 2) \\end{cases} $$"}></span>
						</div>
						<p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #333; word-break: keep-all;">가 $x=2$에서 연속일 때, $a+b$의 값은?</p>
					</div>

					<p style="background: #fffbe6; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #fadb14; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #856404; line-height: 1.6;">
						<b>연속의 정의:</b> <span set:html={mathStep1}></span> 를 이용하여 $a, b$를 찾은 뒤 합을 구합니다.
					</p>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-piecewise/" class="back-link" style="margin-top: 40px; display: inline-block;">← 유형별 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
